The **primary owner** of the parent organization must create a **Compliance Access Key** in [claude.ai > Organization settings > Data and privacy](https://claude.ai/admin-settings/data-privacy-controls) with the following scopes:
- `read:compliance_activities`
- `read:compliance_user_data`
- `read:compliance_org_data`

See [Compliance API Access](https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/manage-claude/compliance-api-access) for full instructions. The key starts with `sk-ant-api01-`.

1. Copy the key into the proxy, as `${path_to_instance_parameters}ADMIN_API_KEY` parameter value in your proxy's host platform.
